<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id78e34e23-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s1015b"><num value="1015b">§ 1015b.</num><heading> Effect of chapter</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Nothing in this chapter affects the applicability of any Federal, State, or local law with respect to any watershed group.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id78e34e24-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/111/11/tVI/s6003">Pub. L. 111–11, title VI, § 6003</ref>, <date date="2009-03-30">Mar. 30, 2009</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/123/1170">123 Stat. 1170</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
